name: Futur Kultur 1.01 (Dreaming of Electric Sheep)
description:
NFXT presents
Jiwosophy x Vuevossa

Futur-kultur (Future Culture) will be a series exploring the marriage of culture and futurism. Featuring the barong mask with a futuristic twist. Backdrop visuals by the local fractal-maestro, Vuevossa. Model, composition and editing by Jiwosophy.
